			<p>The program is a simplefied banking system.  It allows users to log into the system useing their card PIN.  It logs all transactions to a relational database, Microsoft Access, it also manages users failed login attempts and if nessesory confiscate there card and prevent them from accessing the system.</p>
			
			<p><a href="files/portfolio/DatabaseDevelopment.zip">PHP/MySQL Driven Website</a> - This contains a report about web database technologies, service side scripting and databases.  The main focus of these files is the PHP.  The PHP files are simple scripts that run diffrent SQL commands on the MySQL databse.  They add, remove and view data within the database.  The report shows the code in action as well as an entity relationship diagram of the system.</p> 
			
